member.example:
            The following will query on the field "SomeInteger" being equal to 20

Example Json:



            {
                "filter": {
                    "where": {
                        "Key": "SomeInteger",
                        "Operator": "EQ",
                        "Value": 20
                    }
                }
            }



Example C#:



            new SearchQuery()
            {
                Filter = new SearchFilterWhere()
                {
                    Where = new()
                    {
                        Key = nameof(MyDto.SomeInteger),
                        Operator = Operator.EQ,
                        Value = 20
                    }
                }
            }
